WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.750
I was trying to show you all this

00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:04.269
beautiful little squirrel before I

00:00:04.279 --> 00:00:07.790
started. He's

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:11.789
