00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:30.509
there? He's a fat thing;

00:00:30.519 --> 00:00:37.150
he likes french

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:40.790
fries. God is so good. Don't you just love

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:45.270
