00:01:15.479 --> 00:01:20.469
said, 'You must remain hungry;

00:01:20.479 --> 00:01:22.550
keep yourself stirred up for what's

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:25.310
coming, being filled with the Holy

00:01:25.310 --> 00:01:25.320
